{"tid":274642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"80後女生移民紐西蘭實錄：工資不高但賺回生活質素","createTime":"2017-06-07T12:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T11:31:19.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc92996ccb21242ff97244d3380b2ad1b52cfed5","tid":274642,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T12:47:40.000Z","msg":"17:43 2017/06/05<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1825000/1829103/NewZealand20170605ES01BJ_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1825000%2F1829103%2FNewZealand20170605ES01BJ_1024.jpg&h=74019d67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n80後香港女生Roxie，曾在香港當旅遊記者，因工作認識了移民紐西蘭的Johnny。在一年工作假期後，她展開移民紐西蘭之路。<br />\n<br />\nRoxie現於機場免稅店工作之餘，也經營民宿。<br />\n<br />\n她現在拿的是partnership based visa，不論是拍拖情侶或夫婦，都可用家庭團聚形式申請。<br />\n<br />\n另一種是技術移民，比如廚房，醫生、律師，甚至通渠、水電、木工也可，要有相關的學歷和經驗，只要當地有公司聘用，僱主又願意支持，就可申請。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1825000/1829103/NZ09_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1825000%2F1829103%2FNZ09_1024.jpg&h=cefa7811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Roxie的男友Johnny 自11 歲已移民紐西蘭，因緣而成為情侶。（攝影︰馮柏偉）</span><br />\n<br />\n但Roxie提醒，今年紐西蘭提高技術移民的門檻，除了有工作，年薪要達48,000紐元（約26萬港元 ) 以上。<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭北島主要城市是奧克蘭，雖然較發達，但她教路說，要揀移民，南島的基督城較易︰<br />\n<br />\n可以考慮奧克蘭外的地方，如基督城，因之前有大地震又有水災，所有人都走了，嚴重缺乏人材，較易找工作，申請移民也會加分。而修車、通渠、水電、油漆、舖地磚等技術工種，很吃香。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲移民　門檻高於紐西蘭？<br />\n<br />\n近年港人到澳洲工作假期成為潮流，Roxie眼見不少例子，是在當地兩年後返港，不適應之餘又嚮往外國生活，就找移民方法。<br />\n<br />\n鄰國新西蘭氣氛相似，白人國家既講英語又是英聯邦國家。相較而言，澳洲移民門檻較高，起碼要考IELTS試，並要6.5或7分以上。<br />\n之前澳洲也取消了457移民簽證（短期外國勞工），未知未來路向，但肯定會陸續收緊。<br />\n紐西蘭門檻相對易，不一定要考英文試，工作假期也是好選擇，一年名額400個。<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭的樓價如何? <br />\n<br />\nRoxie說紐西蘭樓價很高，當然不可與香港相提並論，比如奧克蘭在市中心，兩房一廳的公寓約售250萬港元，在當地來說已算貴。<br />\n<br />\n我們這處的人工不高，此樓價一般人已很難支付。這處一楝樓，規模如元朗錦繡花園的，要80至100萬紐元(約444萬至555萬港元)。<br />\n但在奧克蘭以外的地區平很多，如2小時車程外的Hamiltion ，可打個8 折，遠一點如Napier等，40至50萬紐元(約220萬至277萬港元)已有交易，還是三房一廳，連車房和花園的。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nRoxie 亦認為，紐西蘭絶非賺錢之地，但是個生活和退休的好地方，紐西蘭最低時薪是15.75紐元，月薪只約萬多港元而已：<br />\n<br />\n但香港可能用10小時換這人工，紐西蘭則用6至8小時。紐西蘭工資不高，但賺回生活質素。<br />\n紐西蘭是否好悶?<br />\n<br />\nRoxie認同紐西蘭是「悶」，時尚潮流大約慢香港3年。但自問是否要買這麼多衫、追求Hi-tech玩意？她認為生活其實不需那麼多，知足常樂才重要：<br />\n<br />\n這處沒得行街看戲或去日本，但我會問香港的朋友，你努力賺錢，籌備退休生活，可能是種花釣魚，那不用等退休，直接來紐西蘭，每天行山釣魚，是很Relax。<br />\n同時，她也經營民宿：<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1825000/1829103/NZ08_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1825000%2F1829103%2FNZ08_1024.JPG&h=75332498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因買這屋有3間房，供樓相當吃力，兩間多餘的做了民宿，租給背包客或短期工作者，雙人房為220紐元(約1,220港元)一星期，單人房125紐元(約694港元)一星期，不是甚麼大錢，卻可幫補供款。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1829103/80%E5%BE%8C%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E7%B4%90%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD%E5%AF%A6%E9%8C%84%EF%BC%9A%E5%B7%A5%E8%B3%87%E4%B8%8D%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%86%E8%B3%BA%E5%9B%9E%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E8%B3%AA%E7%B4%A0?mtc=10011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1829103%2F80%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25B4%2590%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%2598%25AD%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%258C%2584%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25B3%2587%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%25AB%2598%25E4%25BD%2586%25E8%25B3%25BA%25E5%259B%259E%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%25B4%25A0%3Fmtc%3D10011&d=Lwq37QuzZXg%2B2cZCUkfRWI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=1e90a345\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1829103/80%E5%BE%8C%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E7%B4%90%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD%E5%AF%A6%E9%8C%84%EF%BC%9A%E5%B7%A5%E8%B3%87%E4%B8%8D%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%86%E8%B3%BA%E5%9B%9E%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E8%B3%AA%E7%B4%A0?mtc=10011</a>"},{"pid":"ee8b709c181e2117a303e46f7887944e15bb481b","tid":274642,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T12:52:08.000Z","msg":"去紐西蘭係好<br />\n不過要放棄晒香港嘅嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a416dc742c87877ae6a4c46c981b479cce22d704","tid":274642,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:16:00.000Z","msg":"有西就可以移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6e28f471a4eb91ba00dde604d5d2ef55e8a836","tid":274642,"uid":45290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:17:27.000Z","msg":"民宿？<br />\n有冇攞牌先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd36cd9f16e9da9c2b1137c9c58053b5f6df79f","tid":274642,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:20:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>民宿？<br />\n有冇攞牌先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊個話你知澳紐要牌，你喺香港受無良政府趕絶唔代表人哋係"},{"pid":"011a8ae75e4937499894a7134c2773219ecee97c","tid":274642,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:20:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有西就可以移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你一樣可以媾有外國護照嘅女仔㗎"},{"pid":"793135e24d11d7f9dc536a7ae34890bb822890e0","tid":274642,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有西就可以移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你一樣可以媾有外國護照嘅女仔㗎</blockquote><br />\n英文有咁好，我寧願留係香港高薪厚職好過啦。"},{"pid":"b36bc62bfe89f118f248b4c2e192050d280a926a","tid":274642,"uid":93640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:26:01.000Z","msg":"拎左居留權之後就飛左條仔食洋腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7cd4b909a2d6e881da100dbcd31489620ba9769","tid":274642,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:26:18.000Z","msg":"Roxie認同紐西蘭是「悶」，時尚潮流大約慢香港3年。但自問是否要買這麼多衫、追求Hi-tech玩意？她認為生活其實不需那麼多，知足常樂才重要：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdaeec40c0cde0a8e9090cb69ec2c874f26e9f1","tid":274642,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:28:03.000Z","msg":"滾<br />\nbitch"},{"pid":"a4185cfb4e7c382ae8e034952f792ced938d6f9c","tid":274642,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:32:13.000Z","msg":"啱曬毒撚啦 上娘打機之外都冇乜活動"},{"pid":"b867748172fef7898ed55556ede39feb1ee495fa","tid":274642,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:55:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有西就可以移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你一樣可以媾有外國護照嘅女仔㗎</blockquote><br />\n英文有咁好，我寧願留係香港高薪厚職好過啦。</blockquote><br />\n外國一樣有華人嘅"},{"pid":"0c0c76aeebf42fa66492b18a43dfae54c8947e82","tid":274642,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T16:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4acc9736f68a1704a20e0554fdbf63c1ba6e84f","tid":274642,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T16:27:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>民宿？<br />\n有冇攞牌先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊個話你知澳紐要牌，你喺香港受無良政府趕絶唔代表人哋係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭又真係好似唔駛攞牌"},{"pid":"6bf26c258f8b50b18a88fafb797531a1f623e51d","tid":274642,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T16:27:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去紐西蘭係好<br />\n不過要放棄晒香港嘅嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係香港有乜要放棄？"},{"pid":"68afbfbffa3f1fdb19fda4882d9f7c77bef80d55","tid":274642,"uid":107320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:44:59.000Z","msg":"係香港搵到錢但都唔想留係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   地方細人多產業單一食老本，除左搵錢搵唔到理由留係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e3103b23a28f700b0b56fd48f79608f144c35ee","tid":274642,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有西就可以移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你一樣可以媾有外國護照嘅女仔㗎</blockquote><br />\n英文有咁好，我寧願留係香港高薪厚職好過啦。</blockquote><br />\n英文好唔一定高薪厚職<br />\n只不過英文唔好就一定唔會升得好高"},{"pid":"a2b42731fefbc77342d33a3698e35e47d4f5c4e5","tid":274642,"uid":116443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:55:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有西就可以移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你一樣可以媾有外國護照嘅女仔㗎</blockquote><br />\n英文有咁好，我寧願留係香港高薪厚職好過啦。</blockquote><br />\n英文好唔一定高薪厚職<br />\n只不過英文唔好就一定唔會升得好高</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留係香港等訓街？"},{"pid":"4155ba5a1a62ad2766bdf3d305c373c633f9d184","tid":274642,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:58:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有西就可以移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你一樣可以媾有外國護照嘅女仔㗎</blockquote><br />\n英文有咁好，我寧願留係香港高薪厚職好過啦。</blockquote><br />\n英文好唔一定高薪厚職<br />\n只不過英文唔好就一定唔會升得好高</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留係香港等訓街？</blockquote><br />\n絕對支持有能力既移民<br />\n最緊要融入當地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最起碼語言一定要溝通到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1353df597d56bd128fe2d71a85be9cdc4b58c455","tid":274642,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:58:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>民宿？<br />\n有冇攞牌先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊個話你知澳紐要牌，你喺香港受無良政府趕絶唔代表人哋係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩都鐘意管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n發牌"},{"pid":"3c1e0a710230b18ddadfe347f35efb9ef3d6ca55","tid":274642,"uid":1393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:25:14.000Z","msg":"明智抉擇。紐西蘭嘅可持續發展性係全球係排頭幾位。佢地發電大多靠地熱，又注重環境保護，又可以自給自足。佢地目標好似想要做到碳平衡，唔似香港呢D只係講經濟，短視弱智政府。"},{"pid":"2c12abc57cfba37f29425fdb373c6f47fd2ce230","tid":274642,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:31:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cf3cd8043d8cd39a9903afcc54dd928b0f10be0","tid":274642,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T11:31:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>NZ partnership based visa 包唔包same sex couples or partner?</blockquote><br />\n應該包，因紐西蘭容許同性婚姻"}]}